xyz.fsgik.annotations

注释类型 DefaultNonNull


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Nonnull
 @TypeQualifierDefault(value={METHOD,FIELD,PARAMETER,LOCAL_VARIABLE,TYPE_PARAMETER,TYPE_USE})
 @TypeQualifierNickname
 @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR,PACKAGE})
public @interface DefaultNonNull
    Declares the annotated element and all methods, fields parameters, local variables and type uses in its scope must not be null. It is equivalent to use NonNull on those spaces.
